column5: Just wondering if anyone has been up to gullrock the last couple of years, i have not been able to get up there. I am going up there in early june and just wondering what has worked well the last couple years or some good spots to go? any information will be greatly appreciatedgood fishing!!!brad

This will be my 13th year going to Gullrock. We were there the first week of August and it was hot. 93 degrees the first few days. We did well at the point off the high backs, the boot and a weed patch south of the gull rock.
